div.h1: Windows CRLF Handling (\r\n) Scanner Algorithm Trace

p.em: Invariants: Line Tracking and Column Alignment

div.p: char = self.peek() if char == '\n': self.line += 1 self.column = 1 elif char == '\r': # RFC 2046: Treat as transient whitespace # or check for lookahead '\n' self.column += 1 else: self.column += 1 self.ptr += 1
